    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "you also need to set `hierarchicalFacets` on the initialisation:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nvar search = instantsearch({\r\n  //\t...\r\n  searchParameters: {\r\n    hierarchicalFacets: [\r\n      {\r\n        name: \"music_hierarchical.genre.lvl0\",\r\n        attributes: [\r\n          \"music_hierarchical.genre.lvl0\",\r\n          \"music_hierarchical.genre.lvl1\",\r\n          \"music_hierarchical.genre.lvl2\"\r\n        ],\r\n        separator: \" > \"\r\n      }\r\n    ],\r\n    hierarchicalFacetsRefinements: {\r\n      \"music_hierarchical.genre.lvl0\": [\"Rock\"]\r\n    },\r\n    facetingAfterDistinct: true,\r\n    highlightPreTag: \"__ais-highlight__\",\r\n    highlightPostTag: \"__/ais-highlight__\"\r\n  }\r\n});\r\n```\r\n\r\nNote also that the key of the refinement should be the same as the first level.\r\n\r\nI've made a demo of that here: https://codesandbox.io/s/magical-wave-ptgqo",
