    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Note that if you're using InstantSearch v4+ (you seem to be using v1, which is why I gave this solution), you can instead use `initialUiState` like this:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nconst search = instantsearch({\r\n  indexName: 'instant_search',\r\n  searchClient,\r\n  initialUiState: {\r\n    instant_search: {\r\n      hierarchicalMenu: {\r\n        'hierarchicalCategories.lvl0': ['Appliances'],\r\n      },\r\n    },\r\n  },\r\n});\r\n```\r\n\r\ndemo: https://codesandbox.io/s/eloquent-frost-inib5",
